  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Created by a single developer passionate about video games.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Vanity</strong> is a fast-paced third-person shooter (TPS) multiplayer game that throws you into intense battles where every move matters. Whether you enjoy PvP player showdowns or prefer teaming up against waves of enemies in PvE, Vanity delivers a dynamic and varied gameplay experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With more than 10 unique maps and 9 game modes, there’s always a new challenge waiting for you whether you play solo or with a team.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2600670/extras/08d509e7de055742d3beaa881be87d65.poster.avif?t=1757417056\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2600670/extras/08d509e7de055742d3beaa881be87d65.webm?t=1757417056\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2600670/extras/08d509e7de055742d3beaa881be87d65.mp4?t=1757417056\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>PvP & PvE Modes</strong>: Battle other players in intense fights or team up to take down waves of enemies in PvE.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2600670/extras/145db4802405042389818b70bc0a08f3.poster.avif?t=1757417056\" width=1170 height=578 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2600670/extras/145db4802405042389818b70bc0a08f3.webm?t=1757417056\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2600670/extras/145db4802405042389818b70bc0a08f3.mp4?t=1757417056\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Over 10 Maps</strong>: Explore diverse environments where each map requires different strategies.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>9 Game Modes</strong>: Whether you love team matches, deathmatch, objective capture, or more original modes, Vanity has something for you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2600670/extras/fbbe998084c9439b8e1d0c393494682d.poster.avif?t=1757417056\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2600670/extras/fbbe998084c9439b8e1d0c393494682d.webm?t=1757417056\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2600670/extras/fbbe998084c9439b8e1d0c393494682d.mp4?t=1757417056\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Diverse Arsenal</strong>: Wield an arsenal of over 10 different weapons.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2600670/extras/6cec97489fc9f460fafe0b2371f03bdd.poster.avif?t=1757417056\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2600670/extras/6cec97489fc9f460fafe0b2371f03bdd.webm?t=1757417056\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2600670/extras/6cec97489fc9f460fafe0b2371f03bdd.mp4?t=1757417056\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Grenades & Abilities</strong>: Gain the upper hand with multiple grenade types and unique abilities.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Powerful Ultimates</strong>: Unleash spectacular ultimate abilities to turn the tide of battle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2600670/extras/26b2858adba596c83fde4bd537ddcc70.poster.avif?t=1757417056\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2600670/extras/26b2858adba596c83fde4bd537ddcc70.webm?t=1757417056\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2600670/extras/26b2858adba596c83fde4bd537ddcc70.mp4?t=1757417056\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Challenges & Free Rewards</strong>: Complete challenges to unlock free rewards and enhance your gaming experience.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Free Rewards</strong>: Earn free rewards simply by playing! These are frequently updated, giving you fresh items and surprises regularly.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In <strong>Vanity</strong>, every victory brings you one step closer to glory. Show your strategy, agility, and speed to outplay your opponents!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >📺 YouTube: TheLittleGames<br>💬 Discord: TheLittleGames</p>",
